text: Târgovişte is a city in the Dâmboviţa County of Romania. About 89,000 people lived in Târgovişte as of the year 2003. == Twin cities == * Kazanlak, Bulgaria * Targovishte, Bulgaria * Trakai, Lithuania * Orvault, France * Miami, United States * Corbetta, Italy * Santarem, Portugal * Vellinge, Sweden * Castellon de la Plana, Spain Category:Cities in Romania Category:Municipalities of Romania Category:County capitals of Romania Category:Dâmbovița County
